_sText:
2 towers a house and a warehouse and a waterslide

features

waterslide, hidden rooms,  teleporters, ladders and platforms

recomendation

downloaders should explore this map in noclip to find any hidden rooms

all roofs are accessable if you find the hidden ladders and illusion textures

3 teleporters , 2 on warehouse roof back right corner from waterslide
1 to a sky platform 1 to a long drop
and the 3rd from sky platform to a room in the large tower 
if you can't find them contact me on my website www.fubarcs.com and i'll let you know where everything is :)
